data.description: Tastefully updated 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home on CITY WATER. A New Roof was done in 2020, the AC was replaced in 2017, and is upgraded to have a UV HVAC light system. IMPACT RESISTANT Windows and all Exterior Doors, as well as the IMPACT RESISTANT Garage Door with the door screen, were installed in 2017. Beautiful Waterproof Laminate Flooring is throughout (2017). The open and spacious living room has a cathedral ceiling and a New Ceiling Fan (2023). The double-sided sliding door (2017) accesses the sizeable under-truss screened lanai. The KITCHEN was remodeled with a Gorgeous Granite Countertop and Wood Cabinets in 2019. It has plenty of counter space and opens into the living room. The kitchen boasts a double oven electric range, soft-close cabinets, a new kitchen faucet, and ALL stainless-steel appliances. The master bedroom includes an ample walk-in closet, a New Ceiling Fan (2023), and an IMPACT RESISTANT Sliding Door (2017) that accesses the roomy lanai. The bedroom opens into the ensuite bathroom which was completely REMODELED in 2019. The guest bedroom has a New Ceiling Fan (2023) and an adjacent guest bathroom was REMODELED in 2022. The SEPTIC tank was replaced in 2023 and the Hot Water Heater in 2022. The large backyard is fenced and has plenty of room for a pool. The interior and exterior are freshly painted. This beautiful home is located within 3 minutes of I-75 which can take you to any neighboring city: Sarasota 30 minutes, Venice 20 minutes, and Fort Myers 40 minutes. It is close to Hospitals, Golf Courses, and Gulf Coast beaches. There is nothing left to do in this house. Just move in and enjoy.
